    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 16.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第16课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "A Polite Request.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "彬彬有礼的要求。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "listen, and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Traffic police are sometimes very polite.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "交通警察有时非常客气。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "During a holiday in Sweden, I found this note on my car.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "在瑞典度假期间，我在自己的汽车上发现了这张字条。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "Sir, we welcome you to our city.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“先生，欢迎您来到我们的城市。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "This is a no parking area.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这里是禁止停车区。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "You will enjoy your stay here if you pay attention to our street signs.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "如果您留意我们的街道标志，您在这里会过得很愉快。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "This note is only a reminder.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这张字条只是一个提醒。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "If you receive a request like this, you cannot fail to obey it.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "如果你收到这样的要求，就不可能不遵守。"
      }
    }
  ],
